{"tid":2360634,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"傳任天堂Switch Pro今年3月前/下半年推出","createTime":"2021-01-10T03:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T17:00:27.000Z","uid":367280,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1142777fd76c489dbf2e23b0e834f124e22c7523","tid":2360634,"uid":367280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"曾多次爆料任天堂計畫的數據挖掘專家SciresM，日前於論壇4chan貼文稱掌握到Switch Pro的多項訊息，其開發代號為Aula，將搭載OLED螢幕並支援4K解析度，這台高階版Switch會用上代號Mariko的NVIDIA Tegra X1處理器，能透過超頻來實現4K遊戲，由1080p提升到4K對玩家來說，無疑能玩到更高品質的大作。<br />\n此外，亦有消息稱NVIDIA DLSS超高採樣技術也將登陸新Switch，它可透過AI將較低解析度的畫面提升至4K。而產業報導更指出，Switch Pro有可能搭載群創光電的Mini LED螢幕，甚至還傳出會走類似Nintendo 3DS的雙螢幕設計(支持第二屏幕)。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/gadget/20210109/KKTW46GGZVAI5D4L27VQHO3ZFA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fgadget%2F20210109%2FKKTW46GGZVAI5D4L27VQHO3ZFA%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=bf490535\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fgadget%2F20210109%2FKKTW46GGZVAI5D4L27VQHO3ZFA%2F&h=0bf0193a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/gadget/20210109/KKTW46GGZVAI5D4L27VQHO3ZFA/</a>"},{"pid":"956254e69d013e96030f0d497badf229defdfb4a","tid":2360634,"uid":90275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"聖誕都有可能既<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8119a63c1d068b97be577b83df59a75df6e5c3","tid":2360634,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"咁嘅配備要批舊咩電落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7f29d34591fe75226835611a038cc0622b8bbc","tid":2360634,"uid":105822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"又係傳聞<br />\n究竟傳左幾耐"},{"pid":"7afdbd89285a043ce318d570e8a19cb103dbd6c2","tid":2360634,"uid":217433,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6